      "description": "A solid, honest driver with plenty of charm for someone who wants to get in and enjoy the car without paying show-car money. This one is in fair condition, with visible cosmetic wear and the usual signs of age and use, but it still presents respectably overall and has the kind of character that makes it easy to appreciate. A great candidate for weekend cruising, light tinkering, or simply owning and enjoying as-is.",
