      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Runs as a poor-condition example and should be viewed as a project, repair candidate, or possible parts car rather than a clean driver. Expect significant cosmetic wear inside and out, including visible paint/body flaws, a tired interior, and overall age-related deterioration. It may have mechanical needs, deferred maintenance, and issues that should be addressed before regular use, so buyers should plan on repairs and transport/pre-purchase inspection accordingly. Honest car for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at and wants a budget entry point.",
