      "description": "Affordable, honest transportation for the value-focused buyer. This vehicle is best suited for someone seeking a budget-friendly project, basic runabout, or practical stopgap car. It offers straightforward utility at a very accessible price, with plenty of potential for the right owner. Priced to reflect its current condition and to deliver strong value as-is.",
