      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a simple, affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy backup vehicle. If you appreciate a straightforward deal and a car with some life left in it, this one could be a really smart buy. Priced to be fair for what it is, and ready for its next owner.",
